 What is our service?
Moisture Sources and Solutions is a proven provider of warranted, inexpensive, quick and permanent solutions to encapsulate mold, creosote and pet odors. A moisture barrier is formed
without having any unsightly plastic hanging from your walls as a solution. We have an outstanding record with local properties and real estate agents with a 100% SUCCESS AND CUSTOMER
SATISFACTION!
 
MOISTURE SOURCES AND SOLUTIONS, LLC offers a 10 year unconditional transferable warranty:
*All surfaces are properly coated and treated with our exclusive product EnviroMT® which is applied by an approved applicator, and will not support the growth of mold for a period of ten
(10) years.
   


 
 



 
 



 
 



 
 



 
 



 
 

















