Sourcing Solutions

Our mission is to be the trusted alternative to managing the complexity and expense associated with the ever changing lifecycles of IT products. We are the only single source for new End of Life and refurbished IT Hardware across over 25 leading brands. We allow enterprises and data centers to remain standardized on a proven solution delivering eXtension of Life (XOL) solutions that contribute to a superior overall Total Cost of Ownership. Our products all carry industry leading advanced replacement warranty supported by our California based sales and service representatives that are ready to assist.






Industry Leading Alternative IT Solutions


EOL and Refurbished IT Hardware
A great source for End of Life (EOL) and refurbished IT hardware. Attractive pricing and warranties.


NETPATIBLES™
A complete selection of high quality, 100% OEM compatible transceivers, direct attach cables (DAC), and next generation technology for today’s high bandwidth network needs. Savings of up to 80% off the OEM original price. Superior warranties.


Sourcing Engine
Our proprietary turn-key Sourcing Engine delivers a large selection of IT hardware from over 25 leading brands which simplifies purchasing, speeds delivery, and easily obtain support for your purchases.












The Extension of Life Advantage
Today’s IT products can satisfy many end-users requirements well beyond when the OEM manufacturer dictates their End of Life and discontinues their sale of the products. Our commitment to continue to provide these products allows end-users to extend the life of their product deployments improving the total cost of ownership and freeing up capital for other projects.



Single Source for all Alternatives
Comprehensive selection of new and refurbished networking, system, and component products across every major OEM brand, means you won’t have to call multiple suppliers with various levels of quality and support.



Authentication and Validation Firewall
EOL and refurbished products carry an inherent risk of legitimacy and condition classification. That’s why all of our products go through our in-house Authentication and Validation Firewall to ensure our customers are getting exactly what is promised.



Industry Leading Warranties
3 year Advanced Replacement warranty on all networking and system products (1 Year on Components) provides you piece of mind after purchase.









		       IT procurement professionals are increasingly evaluating used-hardware resellers and third-party maintenance providers to reduce costs and extend the functional life of IT assets.
		      

		        Gartner, “Used-Hardware Resellers Offer Hardware and Support Cost Savings”, February, 2015
		      











