Hello











Hello
By: Michael Rubin
Posted: November 30, 2015  | Announcements
Welcome to Sourcing Solutions’ new website! This is our first major redesign since we built the original site in 2012. Future changes and improvements will come much more quickly.
You’ll find our new web site both informative and easy to navigate, whether you’re looking for more information on our End of Life (or what we like to call eXtension of Life) and refurbished IT hardware, or our NETPATIBLES line of 100% compatible transceivers, direct attach cables (DAC), cables, and converters (see more on www.netpatibles.com).   We are just an email or phone call away as the first step in supplying the quality solutions you need.
You can also learn about what we call our Sourcing Solutions Advantage, as we strive to be your sole source for XOL and Refurbished IT hardware.  That’s been part of our mission since the company’s founding in 2010.
Navigate around our website, and you will find photographs and quotes from some of our employees. We’re a great company to do business with and a great place to work.  We strive to provide a challenging, growth-oriented environment that supports work/life balance, and I think we’ve been achieving that.  Also, look for the pictures of Lana, Zoë, and Kaia, part of our four-legged community at Sourcing Solutions.
When we’re in the news, post a press release, or win an award, we’ll let you know on our site. Did you realize that we’re one of the largest women owned businesses in Orange County and named 2015 Top Workplaces in Orange County award by the Orange County Register?
We’d like your input on the site (and our blogs). You can send this to blogger@sourcingsolutions.com   Also, please take the time to hook up with us on LinkedIn, by clicking on the icon below.
Have a happy holidays!
Mike









