About Us

						 We are a dynamic, growing company; a leader in providing and supporting End of Life and Refurbished IT hardware, and innovative OEM compatible advanced networking components, all delivering superior value and lower TCO.
						









Company Overview
Sourcing Solutions LLC is a leader in alternative technology solutions for enterprise and data center operators. The company’s Sourcing Division and Advanced Networking Division offer a wide range of products and services designed to extend the lifecycle of IT products and enhance their value proposition. We offer an extensive catalog of more than 25 brands with more than 50 product categories. We have developed a non-exclusive, turnkey Sourcing Solution to assist us in identifying and delivering solutions to our customers. We have leveraged our experience in sourcing, authenticating, testing, and refurbishing discontinued products that we sell to our channel customers.
Founded in 2010, Sourcing Solutions LLC is headquartered in Costa Mesa, CA where we have a 30,000 square foot facility. Our professional management team of secondary market veterans manages a team of 40+ employees.










